<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="frexp" id="frexp">frexp</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
语法：
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cmath&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">double</span> <span class="kw3">frexp</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> num, <span class="kw4">int</span><span class="sy2">*</span> <span class="kw3">exp</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

函数 frexp() 用来将num分解成两部分：一个介于0.5至1间的尾数(mantissa)（由函数返回）和有exp返回的指数。
科学计数法工作方式如下：
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">     num <span class="sy1">=</span> 尾数 <span class="sy2">*</span> <span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="nu0">2</span> <span class="sy3">^</span> <span class="kw3">exp</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span></pre>
<p>
C++ 也提供了下列重载形式：

</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cmath&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">float</span> <span class="kw3">frexp</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">float</span> num, <span class="kw4">int</span><span class="sy2">*</span> <span class="kw3">exp</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span> <span class="co1">// same as frexpf() in C99</span>
    <span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> <span class="kw3">frexp</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> num, <span class="kw4">int</span><span class="sy2">*</span> <span class="kw3">exp</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span> <span class="co1">// same as frexpl() in C99</span></pre>
<p>
相关主题： <a href="ldexp" class="wikilink1" title="cn:numeric:c:ldexp">ldexp</a>, <a href="modf" class="wikilink1" title="cn:numeric:c:modf">modf</a>
</p>

